n to a goal"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"limit:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EadaA $aA^owFA","text_ar":"عَدَا شَاْوًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaraY $aA^owFA","text_ar":"جَرَى شَاْوًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a horse, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ran a heat"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"him~apN","text_ar":"هِمَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": thus in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahu labaEiydu Al$~aA^owi","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُ لَبَعِيدُ الشَّاْوِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily he is far-aiming,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"far-aspiring, in purpose, desire,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ambition"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Lh, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saA^owN","text_ar":"سَاْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a dial. var. thereof. (TA.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"basket such as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zabiyl","text_ar":"زَبِيل"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mi$oA=pN","text_ar":"مِشْا=ةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zabiyl","text_ar":"زَبِيل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which the earth of a well is taken forth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the measure of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mi$oEaApN","text_ar":"مِشْعَاةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$aA='K","text_ar":"مَشَا=ءٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aA^owN","text_ar":"شَاْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies, (S,) or signifies also, (K,) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"earth that is taken forth from a well"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the like of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mi$oA=p","text_ar":"مِشْا=ة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (as in a copy of the S,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as fills the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"m$oA=p","text_ar":"مشْا=ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (so in another copy of the S [agreeably with what next follows]:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zabiyl","text_ar":"زَبِيل"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the earth of a well."},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, T, TA.) ―         -b2-  And hence, i. e. as being likened to a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zbyl","text_ar":"زبيل"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the earth of a well, (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dung that the he-ass and the she-ass casts forth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, T, TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dung"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the she-camel; (M, K;) but the more approved word is ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saA^owN","text_ar":"سَاْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"s","text_ar":"س"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, TA.)       -A3-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nose-rein"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zimaAm","text_ar":"زِمَام"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a she-camel."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","Lh","TA","K","As","T"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}